briefdescription.para: If there is a science cluster registered that this Part belongs to - we check further. Without a science cluster - we can't transmit. Then will try to find the controller module and check it's enabled along with this module and that the whole cluster is powered. Returns the state of this module + the controller module and if the entire science cluster is powered.
Is active, but called when the vessel is unloaded. This is called on the prefab module on the part prefab and passed the ProtoPartModuleSnapshot on the relevant unloaded vessel.

parameterdescription.para: The ProtoPartModuleSnapshot of the partmodule on the relevant vessel

briefdescription.para: Used by CommNetVessel to determine best antenna to use to transmit science. But as Deployed Science - ModuleGroundCommsPart's Cannot be used for regular science transmissions. This will always return false.
Returns the Comm Power for Unloaded Vessel/Part. Will combine additional Sat Booster Parts if they are in the deployed science cluster.
